<td tEditID="c1r1" style="width:600px;min-width:600px;background-color:#F0EBE3;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:14px;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0">
<![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-CA">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"/></head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#F0EBE3;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">
<div style="display:none;font-size:1px;color:#F0EBE3;line-height:1px;max-height:0;max-width:0;opacity:0;overflow:hidden;mso-hide:all;">Come on in.</div>
<!--[if mso]><table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center"><tr><td><![endif]-->
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="600" align="center" style="width:600px;min-width:600px;margin:0 auto;background-color:#F0EBE3;">
<tr><td style="padding:24px 0 0;">
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="600" style="width:600px;min-width:600px;">
<tr><td style="background-color:#FAF7F2;padding:14px 24px;border-radius:8px 8px 0 0;border-bottom:1px solid #E8E0D6;">
<a href="https://our.fimby.com" style="text-decoration:none;"><img src="https://our.fimby.com/sfsites/c/resource/Impact_Icons/FIMBYwGrass.png" height="40" alt="FIMBY" style="border:0;display:block;"/></a>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="background-color:#FAF7F2;padding:20px 24px 16px;border-radius:0 0 8px 8px;">
<p style="margin:0;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#2D2D2D;line-height:1.35;">Welcome to the family in your backyard</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:16px 0 20px;">
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="600" style="width:600px;min-width:600px;"><tr><td style="background:#FFFFFF;border-radius:8px;padding:18px 24px;border:1px solid #E8E0D6;border-left:3px solid #5B8760;">
<p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#4A4A4A;line-height:1.55;">Hi {!Receiving_User.FirstName},</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#4A4A4A;line-height:1.55;">For years I&apos;ve been dreaming about this &mdash; a simple way to help neighbours know and care for each other, rooted in the belief that a more beautiful world is possible when we treat each other with love and generosity.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#4A4A4A;line-height:1.55;">That dream is FIMBY, and you&apos;re now part of it.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#4A4A4A;line-height:1.55;">This is a grand experiment in neighbouring. We&apos;re building something together &mdash; a place where we look out for each other, share what we have, and show up when it matters. Not perfectly. But together.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#4A4A4A;line-height:1.55;">Welcome to the family in your backyard.</p>
<p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#4A4A4A;line-height:1.55;">Use the button below to set your password and come on in. This link is for you only and expires after a short time. Your username is <strong>{!Receiving_User.Username}</strong>.</p>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin:0 0 18px;"><tr><td align="center">
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td style="background:#3A7D8C;border-radius:12px;padding:12px 28px;">
<a href="{!Community_Url}" style="color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:none;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Come on in</a>
</td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin:0;"><tr>
<td style="vertical-align:top;padding-right:16px;">
<a href="https://our.fimby.com/sfsites/c/resource/Impact_Icons/StephenRathjen.JPEG" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="text-decoration:none;">
<img src="https://our.fimby.com/sfsites/c/resource/Impact_Icons/StephenRathjen.JPEG" width="96" height="128" alt="Stephen Rathjen" style="display:block;border:0;border-radius:8px;max-width:96px;height:auto;"/>
</a>
</td>
<td style="vertical-align:top;">
<p style="margin:0;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#4A4A4A;line-height:1.55;">With love,<br/>Stephen Rathjen<br/><span style="color:#6B6B6B;font-size:13px;">Founder, FIMBY</span></p>
</td>
</tr></table>
</td></tr></table>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="background-color:#FAF7F2;padding:16px 24px 24px;border-radius:8px;border-top:1px solid #E8E0D6;">
<p style="margin:0;font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#6B6B6B;"><a href="https://fimby.com" style="color:#3A7D8C;text-decoration:none;">Family In My Backyard</a> &middot; <a href="https://fimby.com/our-approach/" style="color:#3A7D8C;text-decoration:none;">Our approach</a></p>
</td></tr>
</table>
</td></tr>
</table>
